com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface WindowsLocalUser

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, User
All Known Implementing Classes:
WindowsLocalUserImpl
public interface WindowsLocalUser
extends User

A representation of the model object 'Windows Local User'.

The following features are supported:

  • Account Description
  • Account Disabled
  • Account Locked
  • Change Password Next Logon
  • Enable Remote Control
  • Full Name
  • Home Folder
  • Logon Script
  • Password Never Expires
  • Profile Path
  • User Account Type
  • User Cannot Change Password
  • User Sid
  • User Sid Type

See Also:
OsPackage.getWindowsLocalUser()
